OL,3,CJon Boutcher condemns those who
OL,4,Ccarried out bomb attack attempt as
OL,5,C'cowards'
OL,7,FThe proxy bomb attack attempt on a
OL,8,Fpolice station is a "timely reminder"
OL,9,Fof the terrorist threat level in
OL,10,FNorthern Ireland, the PSNI Chief
OL,11,FConstable has said.
OL,13,FJon Boutcher condemned those who
OL,14,Fcarried out the attack as "cowards"
OL,15,Fand said dissident republican groups
OL,16,F"have no support and nothing to offer".
OL,26,@pD@UOUpD@eO]vD@[OUvD@cO]xD@AOUxD@fO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/10
