PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F449A1775426988
OL,3,CJon Boutcher condemns those who
OL,4,Ccarried out bomb attack attempt as
OL,5,C'cowards'
OL,7,FDissident republicans have been blamed
OL,8,Ffor the incident in Lurgan earlier
OL,9,Fthis week when a food delivery driver
OL,10,Fwas hijacked in Kilwilkie and forced
OL,11,Fto drive a "crude but viable" device
OL,12,Fto the station.
OL,14,FIt has been roundly condemned by
OL,15,Fpolitical leaders across Northern
OL,16,FIreland.
OL,26,@sD@LOUsD@]O]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/10
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
