FL,450,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F449A1775426988
OL,3,CJon Boutcher condemns those who
OL,4,Ccarried out bomb attack attempt as
OL,5,C'cowards'
OL,7,FMr Boutcher said the incident is
OL,8,F"likely to have been a sad attempt to
OL,9,Fappear relevant ahead of planned
OL,10,Fdissident Republican parades over
OL,11,FEaster".
OL,13,FThe 1916 rising is marked annually as
OL,14,Fone of the events leading to the
OL,15,Findependence of the Republic of
OL,16,FIreland from British rule in 1922.
OL,26,@pD@AOUsD@GO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/10
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,450,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F449A1775426988
OL,3,CJon Boutcher condemns those who
OL,4,Ccarried out bomb attack attempt as
OL,5,C'cowards'
OL,7,FMr Boutcher told the policing board on
OL,8,FThursday that investigation into the
OL,9,Fattack is ongoing but "there is little
OL,10,Fdoubt that dissident Republicans were
OL,11,Fresponsible".
OL,13,F"The only thing these people are
OL,14,Finterested in is themselves and their
OL,15,Fown egos," he said.
OL,17,F"They are irrelevant to today's
OL,18,Fcommunities in Northern Ireland.
OL,26,@qD@WOUsD@LO]uD@AOUwD@JO]yD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/10
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,450,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F449A1775426988
OL,3,CJon Boutcher condemns those who
OL,4,Ccarried out bomb attack attempt as
OL,5,C'cowards'
OL,7,F"I want to pay particular tribute to
OL,8,Fthe courageous delivery driver who
OL,9,Falerted officers to the threat, and
OL,10,Fask that people consider the contrast
OL,11,Fbetween the cowards that perpetrated
OL,12,Fthis and that delivery driver and all
OL,13,Fthose countless people in our society
OL,14,Fwho repeatedly stand up against such
OL,15,Funsupported acts of terrorism or acts
OL,16,Fof intimidation.
OL,26,@oD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G5/10
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,450,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44906
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F449A1775426988
OL,3,CJon Boutcher condemns those who
OL,4,Ccarried out bomb attack attempt as
OL,5,C'cowards'
OL,7,F"There is no place in a democratic
OL,8,Fsociety for such criminals and I
OL,9,Fappeal to anyone with any information
OL,10,Fwhatsoever to come forward and tell us
OL,11,Fwhat they know, tell us who was
OL,12,Finvolved before these idiots cause
OL,13,Fsome harm.
OL,15,F"They do not deserve anyone's
OL,16,Fprotection or support.
OL,18,F"It's been some time since the Chief
OL,19,FConstable has come before this board
OL,20,Fin the aftermath of a dissident
OL,21,FRepublican attack towards our officers.
OL,26,@oD@AOUwD@AOUzD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G6/10
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,450,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44907
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F449A1775426988
OL,3,CJon Boutcher condemns those who
OL,4,Ccarried out bomb attack attempt as
OL,5,C'cowards'
OL,7,F"These events are a timely reminder
OL,8,Fthat the threat level in Northern
OL,9,FIreland remains at substantial meaning
OL,10,Fat any time an attack is likely.
OL,12,F"PSNI officers and staff are still the
OL,13,Fprimary target of that threat."
OL,15,FHe went on to describe the attempted
OL,16,Fattack as being "as futile as it was
OL,17,Fcruel".
OL,26,@oD@AOUtD@AOUuD@_O]xD@QOUyD@FO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G7/10
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,450,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44908
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F449A1775426988
OL,3,CJon Boutcher condemns those who
OL,4,Ccarried out bomb attack attempt as
OL,5,C'cowards'
OL,7,F"These ever decreasing dissident gangs
OL,8,Fhave no support and nothing to offer.
OL,9,FSociety simply does not want them," he
OL,10,Fsaid.
OL,12,F"The sooner they realise that the
OL,13,Fbetter and things will be much better
OL,14,Ffor everyone.
OL,16,F"I ask all such groups to stop such
OL,17,Fpointless attacks. You are changing
OL,18,Fnothing."
OL,26,@oD@AOUqD@cO]tD@AOUxD@AOUzD@IO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G8/10
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
