PN,44909
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F449A1775426988
OL,3,CJon Boutcher condemns those who
OL,4,Ccarried out bomb attack attempt as
OL,5,C'cowards'
OL,7,FThe Chief Constable also told the
OL,8,Fboard about a letter he received from
OL,9,Fa social worker who spent Christmas
OL,10,FEve in a police station with a mother
OL,11,Fand "two traumatised children" after a
OL,12,Fdomestic abuse incident, to commend
OL,13,Fthe "patience, care, empathy and
OL,14,Funderstanding" shown by officers.
OL,16,F"Those who attacked Lurgan police
OL,17,Fstation should reflect on those
OL,18,Fstations being a place of safety for
OL,19,Fvulnerable people," he said.
OL,26,@sD@EOUsD@^O]uD@EOUvD@NO]xD@AOU{D@SO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G9/10
